{"image_id": "SBAC_2011_page_113", "image_size": [1275, 1650], "ocr": [{"text": "Table of Contents", "bbox": [37.5, 90.6, 206.4, 119.3]}, {"text": "SBA COMMUNICATIONS CORPORATION AND SUBSIDIARIES", "bbox": [329.5, 143.2, 955.9, 172.1]}, {"text": "NOTES TO CONSOLIDATED FINANCIAL STATEMENTS", "bbox": [362.0, 166.4, 923.4, 195.3]}, {"text": "Operating Leases and Capital Leases", "bbox": [85.5, 239.2, 414.2, 267.7]}, {"text": "The Company is obligated under various non-cancelable operating leases for land, office space, equipment and site leases that expire at", "bbox": [85.5, 271.7, 1218.2, 299.3]}, {"text": "various times through August 2111. In addition, the Company is obligated under various non-cancelable capital leases for vehicles that expire", "bbox": [37.5, 294.7, 1224.7, 322.3]}, {"text": "at various times through December 2015. The amounts applicable to capital leases for vehicles included in property and equipment, net were:", "bbox": [37.5, 317.9, 1226.9, 345.6]}, {"text": "The annual minimum lease payments under non-cancelable operating and capital leases in effect as of December 31, 2011 are as follows", "bbox": [85.5, 513.7, 1229.7, 541.3]}, {"text": "(in thousands):", "bbox": [37.5, 536.9, 172.4, 564.6]}, {"text": "Future minimum rental payments under noncancelable ground leases include payments for certain renewal periods at the Company’s", "bbox": [85.5, 896.7, 1197.9, 924.3]}, {"text": "option because failure to renew could result in a loss of the applicable tower site and related revenue from tenant leases, thereby making it", "bbox": [37.5, 919.9, 1193.9, 947.6]}, {"text": "reasonably assured that the Company will renew the lease. The majority of operating leases provide for renewal at varying escalations. Fixed", "bbox": [37.5, 942.9, 1218.2, 970.6]}, {"text": "rate escalations have been included in the table disclosed above.", "bbox": [37.5, 965.9, 582.4, 993.6]}, {"text": "Rent expense for operating leases was $82.8 million, $75.4 million and $72.6 million for the years ended December 31, 2011, 2010 and", "bbox": [85.5, 1007.9, 1221.9, 1035.6]}, {"text": "2009, respectively. In addition, certain of the Company’s leases include contingent rent provisions which provide for the lessor to receive", "bbox": [37.5, 1030.9, 1188.2, 1058.6]}, {"text": "additional rent upon the attainment of certain tower operating results and or lease-up. Contingent rent expense for the years ended", "bbox": [37.5, 1053.9, 1124.4, 1081.6]}, {"text": "December 31, 2011, 2010 and 2009 was $13.7 million, $12.5 million and $9.9 million, respectively.", "bbox": [37.5, 1076.9, 882.4, 1104.6]}, {"text": "Capital Lease Obligations", "bbox": [85.5, 1128.2, 318.2, 1156.7]}, {"text": "The Company’s capital lease obligations outstanding were $3.1 million as of December 31, 2011 and $1.5 million as of December 31,", "bbox": [85.5, 1160.7, 1208.4, 1188.3]}, {"text": "2010. As of December 31, 2011, these obligations bore interest rates ranging from 0.2% to 3.2% and will mature in periods ranging from", "bbox": [37.5, 1183.7, 1185.4, 1211.3]}, {"text": "approximately one to five years.", "bbox": [37.5, 1206.9, 316.9, 1234.6]}, {"text": "F-41", "bbox": [617.7, 1247.4, 662.2, 1275.1]}, {"text": "20.", "bbox": [37.5, 207.1, 68.7, 235.8]}, {"text": "COMMITMENTS AND CONTINGENCIES", "bbox": [85.5, 207.1, 489.9, 235.8]}, {"text": "As of", "bbox": [762.5, 364.3, 804.9, 385.8]}, {"text": "December 31, 2011", "bbox": [716.2, 381.8, 863.1, 403.3]}, {"text": "As of", "bbox": [1000.5, 364.3, 1042.9, 385.8]}, {"text": "December 31, 2010", "bbox": [954.2, 381.8, 1088.9, 403.3]}, {"text": "(in thousands)", "bbox": [851.0, 400.1, 950.4, 421.5]}, {"text": "Vehicles", "bbox": [181.5, 416.4, 259.4, 444.1]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [716.2, 416.4, 731.7, 444.1]}, {"text": "5,546", "bbox": [796.5, 416.4, 863.1, 444.1]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [954.2, 416.4, 969.7, 444.1]}, {"text": "3,110", "bbox": [1034.5, 416.4, 1096.7, 444.1]}, {"text": "Less: accumulated depreciation"